                class="text-bold">ALL
                SERVICES ARE FINAL SALE.</span></p>
    </section>
    <footer style="margin:4em 0em;" class="text-bold d-flex background-grey">
        <div class="p-1">SIGN</div>
        <div class="p-1">DATE</div>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>